-- ICA Mulls Purchase of Homebuilder Javer, Excelsior’s Celis Says
-- B y   C a r l o s   M a n u e l   R o d r i g u e z
-- 2012-06-07T13:06:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-07/ica-mulls-purchase-of-homebuilder-javer-excelsior-s-celis-says.html
Empresas ICA SAB (ICA*) ,  Mexico ’s largest
construction company, is evaluating the acquisition of Servicios
Corporativos Javer SAPI, Excelsior newspaper  reported .  ICA wants to boost its housing unit known as Viveica
through an acquisition, Dario Celis, a columnist for the Mexico-
City based newspaper, wrote today, citing company sources he did
not identify.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Carlos Manuel Rodriguez in Mexico City at 
